pageProduct.name: SUP Shots Daily Essentials 8x50ml Vials
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Essential daily nutrients: Vitamins B & C, Probiotics and Antioxidants.

DAILY PICK ME UP
For times when you want to order that extra coffee, snooze the alarm or hit that 3pm slump reach for a SUP Daily Essentials instead. With B Vitamins for energy, Vitamin C for immune support, Berries rich in Antioxidants and Probiotics for digestive goodness. It's your all-rounder daily performance hero.

WHY SHOT SUP?
Drink your supplements on-the-go with our super shots. SUP is formulated with essential day to day ingredients to help:
  • Support daily vitality and wellness
  • Minimise tiredness and fatigue with B6
  • Boost energy levels with B12
  • Boost immune health with Vitamin C
SHOTSUP

Size: 8x50mL

KEY FEATURES

• Support daily vitality and wellness
• Minimise tiredness and fatigue with B6
• Boost energy levels with B12
• Boost immune health with Vitamin C

Warnings

The food is not a sole source of nutrition and should be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and exercise program. Not suitable for children under 15 years of age or pregnant women. Should be used under medical or dietetic supervision. Do not use if tamper evidence seal is broken or missing. Store below 25?°C.

Ingredients

Water, Apple juice concentrate, Fresh ginseng extract, Sweeteners (erythritol, steviol glycoside), Elderberry powder, Noni juice, L-Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C), Natural grape flavour, Flavour (citric acid monohydrate), Stabiliser (HM Pectin), Inulin, Natural raspberry flavour, Calcium pantothenate (Vitamin B5), Goji extract, Niacinamide (Vitamin B3), Mangosteen extract, Bacillus coagulans, Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12), Pyridoxine hydrochloride (Vitamin B6), Thiamine mononitrate (Vitamin B1).

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Peanuts

Directions

Shot 1 SUP (50mL) for that daily pick me up. Up to 3 weeks supply

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
